## 🧠 Course Overview

> Master Python by building 100 projects in 100 days.  
> Learn data science, automation, web development, games, and more — all in one bootcamp.

This hands-on course by **Dr. Angela Yu** follows the **#100DaysOfCode** challenge format.  
Every day, you’ll tackle a new Python project — from beginner tasks to professional apps.

🎓 **Course link:** [100 Days of Code: The Complete Python Pro Bootcamp](https://www.udemy.com/course/100-days-of-code/?couponCode=MT251015G4)

---

## 📚 What You’ll Learn

✅ Write professional Python code  
✅ Automate everyday tasks  
✅ Build games (🎲 Blackjack, 🐍 Snake, 🏓 Pong)  
✅ Create web apps with Flask  
✅ Scrape websites with BeautifulSoup and Selenium  
✅ Work with data science libraries: Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib  
✅ Design APIs and backend systems  
✅ Build GUIs and desktop apps  
✅ Deploy apps to Heroku and GitHub Pages  
✅ Master version control with Git & GitHub  

---

## 💻 Requirements

- No prior coding experience needed 🙌  
- A 64-bit computer (Mac, PC, or Linux)  
- Internet access  
- All tools are **free or open-source**  
- Step-by-step setup provided by the instructor  

---

## 🏗️ Course Structure

📆 **Duration:** 100 Days  
💡 **Format:** Project-based learning  
🎥 **Content:** HD video lectures, challenges, quizzes  
🧩 **Output:** 100 complete projects for your portfolio  

Each day builds upon the previous — so you grow your skills gradually while keeping things practical and fun.

---

## 🧭 How to Succeed

🔥 Commit to at least **1 hour of coding per day**  
🧩 Code along with the instructor  
📝 Document your learning and progress  
💬 Engage in community discussions  
📈 Push your projects to GitHub  
💡 Refactor old projects as you improve  

---

## 💼 Portfolio Project Examples

| Category | Example Projects |
|-----------|------------------|
| 🎮 Games | Blackjack, Snake, Pong |
| 🧠 Automation | Email sender, data cleaner, web scraper |
| 🌐 Web Dev | Personal blog, REST API, portfolio site |
| 📊 Data Science | Data visualization dashboards |
| 💻 Desktop Apps | GUI utilities with Tkinter |

> 💼 By the end, you’ll have 100 projects to showcase on your résumé or portfolio.

---

## ⚙️ Tools & Technologies

| Area | Tools / Libraries |
|------|--------------------|
| Core | Python 3, PyCharm, Jupyter Notebook |
| Web Dev | Flask, HTML, CSS, Bootstrap |
| Data | Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, Plotly, scikit-learn |
| Automation | BeautifulSoup, Selenium, Requests |
| Databases | SQLite, PostgreSQL |
| Version Control | Git & GitHub |
| Deployment | Heroku, GitHub Pages |

